00:12:52,030 --> 00:12:53,260
That cultural dealer

300
00:12:53,320 --> 00:12:55,290
drove off the cliff and died.

301
00:12:55,390 --> 00:12:58,790
I heard the leader
was Chief Zhang from the Municipal Bureau.

302
00:13:01,390 --> 00:13:01,840
Uncle.

303
00:13:04,620 --> 00:13:06,190
I will get your revenge.

304
00:13:15,200 --> 00:13:16,000
What's going on?

305
00:13:16,000 --> 00:13:16,930
What's going on?

306
00:13:26,960 --> 00:13:27,630
Raise your arms.

307
00:13:27,630 --> 00:13:28,360
Turn around.

308
00:13:29,000 --> 00:13:29,930
Raise your arms.

309
00:13:33,790 --> 00:13:34,200
Go.

310
00:13:34,270 --> 00:13:35,000
Turn around.

311
00:13:36,630 --> 00:13:37,120
Next.

312
00:13:39,200 --> 00:13:39,600
Here.

313
00:13:44,510 --> 00:13:45,570
Turn around. Next.

314
00:13:47,750 --> 00:13:48,390
Here. Go.

315
00:13:54,120 --> 00:13:54,920
Open your bag.

316
00:13:55,000 --> 00:13:55,510
Next.

317
00:13:55,550 --> 00:13:56,160
Go.

318
00:13:56,240 --> 00:13:56,630
Hey.

319
00:13:56,790 --> 00:13:57,720
Why are you cutting the queue?

320
00:13:57,720 --> 00:13:58,250
Exactly.

321
00:13:58,990 --> 00:13:59,920
Raise your arms.

322
00:14:03,150 --> 00:14:03,810
Okay. Next.

323
00:14:05,550 --> 00:14:06,390
Hurry up.

324
00:14:06,960 --> 00:14:08,000
Raise your arms.

325
00:14:08,550 --> 00:14:09,270
I've been

326
00:14:09,270 --> 00:14:10,870
coughing for a week.

327
00:14:11,510 --> 00:14:12,240
Turn around.

328
00:14:13,320 --> 00:14:14,670
Is it pneumonia?

329
00:14:14,720 --> 00:14:16,180
Go see the doctor quickly.

330
00:14:19,840 --> 00:14:20,440
Next.

331
00:14:26,550 --> 00:14:27,480
Raise your arms.

332
00:14:27,790 --> 00:14:28,790
Whose bag is this?

333
00:14:29,360 --> 00:14:30,200
Mine.

334
00:14:31,390 --> 00:14:32,190
What's wrong?

335
00:14:32,270 --> 00:14:33,320
What happened?

336
00:14:33,750 --> 00:14:34,910
What about this knife?

337
00:14:34,910 --> 00:14:36,440
That's not mine.

338
00:14:36,510 --> 00:14:38,000
I didn't put this in.

339
00:14:38,270 --> 00:14:39,150
Tell the truth.

340
00:14:39,240 --> 00:14:39,770
Hey.

341
00:14:39,870 --> 00:14:41,200
Look at the state I'm in.

342
00:14:41,200 --> 00:14:42,270
Why should I carry a knife?

343
00:14:42,270 --> 00:14:43,200
I'm calling the police.

344
00:14:43,200 --> 00:14:44,510
Don't, I have an exam this afternoon.

345
00:14:44,510 --> 00:14:45,310
Take him away.

346
00:14:45,320 --> 00:14:45,630
Hey!

347
00:14:45,720 --> 00:14:46,440
What are you doing?

348
00:14:46,440 --> 00:14:47,360
I really have an exam this afternoon.

349
00:14:47,360 --> 00:14:48,270
I'll be late!

350
00:15:01,290 --> 00:15:02,310
[4th floor]

351
00:15:02,310 --> 00:15:03,670
[Surgery Room]

352
00:15:22,600 --> 00:15:23,660
Don't be nervous.

353
00:15:24,150 --> 00:15:25,080
I'm not nervous.

354
00:15:30,480 --> 00:15:32,550
Starting now, count to 10.

355
00:15:33,390 --> 00:15:34,190
When?

356
00:15:34,320 --> 00:15:35,270
Now.

357
00:15:37,390 --> 00:15:38,470
One....

358
00:15:42,750 --> 00:15:43,480
That's fast.

359
00:15:44,030 --> 00:15:45,270
That was a normal dosage.

360
00:15:45,270 --> 00:15:45,960
Okay.

361
00:15:53,030 --> 00:15:54,080
Where's this from?

362
00:15:54,080 --> 00:15:54,960
Someone tried to bring

363
00:15:54,960 --> 00:15:55,870
a knife in at the security check.

364
00:15:55,870 --> 00:15:56,750
They stopped him.

365
00:15:56,750 --> 00:15:57,460
Huo Zheng?

366
00:15:57,840 --> 00:15:58,320
No.

367
00:15:58,390 --> 00:15:59,750
Someone's trying to cause trouble?

368
00:15:59,750 --> 00:16:01,610
He insisted the knife wasn't his.

369
00:16:01,670 --> 00:16:02,200
If not his,

370
00:16:02,200 --> 00:16:03,800
did someone put it in his bag?

371
00:16:04,510 --> 00:16:05,030
Could it be

372
00:16:05,030 --> 00:16:06,360
Huo Zheng has sneaked in

373
00:16:06,910 --> 00:16:08,510
and is trying to distract us?

374
00:16:10,000 --> 00:16:10,460
Li Qian.

375
00:16:10,550 --> 00:16:11,320
You two stay here.

376
00:16:11,320 --> 00:16:11,630
Okay.

377
00:16:11,630 --> 00:16:12,360
Get the SWAT back.

378
00:16:12,360 --> 00:16:12,600
Yes.

379
00:16:12,600 --> 00:16:13,840
The rest of you, follow me.

380
00:16:13,840 --> 00:16:14,970
No matter what it is,

381
00:16:15,000 --> 00:16:16,460
don't let your guard down.

382
00:16:31,550 --> 00:16:32,060
Hurry!

383
00:16:42,340 --> 00:16:44,390
[Infusion Room]

384
00:16:45,240 --> 00:16:46,240
Check over there.

385
00:16:46,270 --> 00:16:46,750
Follow me.

386
00:16:46,750 --> 00:16:47,150
Okay.

387
00:16:49,290 --> 00:16:53,550
[Please keep quiet]

388
00:16:54,200 --> 00:16:54,910
You go this way.

389
00:16:54,910 --> 00:16:55,460
Okay.

390
00:16:56,400 --> 00:17:02,160
[Please keep quiet] [Infusion Room]

391
00:17:05,109 --> 00:17:08,760
[Please keep quiet] [Infusion Room]

392
00:17:14,720 --> 00:17:16,920
Hou Shengjie's skin test result is out.

393
00:17:26,400 --> 00:17:27,530
I'll be right there.

394
00:17:45,650 --> 00:17:47,880
[Infusion Room]

395
00:18:08,030 --> 00:18:09,230
Hou Shengjie, right?

396
00:18:11,160 --> 00:18:12,070
You're not allergic to penicillin,

397
00:18:12,070 --> 00:18:12,530
are you?

398
00:18:12,590 --> 00:18:13,070
I am.

399
00:18:14,510 --> 00:18:15,510
The test result shows

400
00:18:15,510 --> 00:18:17,200
you're not allergic to penicillin.

401
00:18:17,200 --> 00:18:18,530
Are you allergic or not?

402
00:18:19,960 --> 00:18:20,640
No.

403
00:18:24,910 --> 00:18:25,970
I'll verify again.

404
00:18:26,440 --> 00:18:27,200
Hou Shengjie,

405
00:18:27,200 --> 00:18:29,800
you're not not allergic to penicillin,
right?

406
00:18:41,880 --> 00:18:42,540
Don't move.

407
00:18:44,790 --> 00:18:45,590
Stop looking.

408
00:18:45,750 --> 00:18:46,810
Go keep an eye on the surgery room.

409
00:18:46,810 --> 00:18:47,810
Wait for the SWAT.

410
00:18:55,310 --> 00:18:55,760
Done.

411
00:19:19,200 --> 00:19:19,810
What?

412
00:19:32,640 --> 00:19:33,480
The SWAT is here.

413
00:19:33,480 --> 00:19:35,410
They're searching them one by one.

414
00:19:35,510 --> 00:19:36,590
Don't make too much noise.

415
00:19:36,590 --> 00:19:38,050
Don't scare the patients.

416
00:19:53,550 --> 00:19:55,020
One, two, three.

417
00:20:07,700 --> 00:20:12,930
[Surgery Room]

418
00:20:11,880 --> 00:20:12,270
Doctor!

419
00:20:12,270 --> 00:20:12,730
Doctor!

420
00:20:13,030 --> 00:20:13,560
How is it?

421
00:20:13,590 --> 00:20:14,680
The surgery went well.

422
00:20:14,250 --> 00:20:15,270
[Entrance Access Card]

423
00:20:14,720 --> 00:20:15,400
Don't worry.

424
00:20:15,400 --> 00:20:16,160
Just treat it

425
00:20:16,160 --> 00:20:17,310
as an ordinary appendicitis surgery.

426
00:20:17,310 --> 00:20:18,490
But it's not a minor trauma.

427
00:20:18,490 --> 00:20:19,510
So Chief Zhang's all right?

428
00:20:19,510 --> 00:20:19,960
He's fine.

429
00:20:19,960 --> 00:20:20,750
He'll come out

430
00:20:20,750 --> 00:20:21,750
when the anesthesia wears off.

431
00:20:21,750 --> 00:20:22,550
Thank you.

432
00:20:22,550 --> 00:20:23,260
-Thank you.
-Thank you.

433
00:20:23,260 --> 00:20:24,590
-Thank you.
-Thank you.

434
00:20:26,240 --> 00:20:27,060
It's fine now.

435
00:20:29,830 --> 00:20:30,290
Well...

436
00:20:31,350 --> 00:20:33,010
We still can't go in, it seems.

437
00:20:58,110 --> 00:20:58,750
Two...

438
00:22:03,590 --> 00:22:04,390
Captain Wang!

439
00:22:04,920 --> 00:22:05,680
Captain Wang.

440
00:22:05,680 --> 00:22:07,350
A doctor was knocked out in the toilet.

441
00:22:07,350 --> 00:22:09,210
His surgical uniform was stolen.

442
00:22:11,880 --> 00:22:12,680
Open the door!

443
00:22:13,270 --> 00:22:14,070
Open the door!

444
00:22:30,750 --> 00:22:33,310
How did you... get in?

445
00:22:35,750 --> 00:22:36,400
What are you doing?

446
00:22:36,400 --> 00:22:37,330
This is the surgery room.

447
00:22:37,330 --> 00:22:38,590
Where is Zhang Yi'ang?

448
00:22:38,920 --> 00:22:40,050
Tell me, where is he?

449
00:22:48,830 --> 00:22:49,620
I...

450
00:22:50,030 --> 00:22:50,960
will kill you...

451
00:22:52,190 --> 00:22:55,070
to avenge... avenge...

452
00:22:55,160 --> 00:22:56,700
Uncle Yifei.

453
00:23:01,030 --> 00:23:02,830
You scoundrel.

454
00:23:05,640 --> 00:23:07,490
Try it if you dare.

455
00:23:07,550 --> 00:23:10,590
Don't try me.

456
00:23:11,570 --> 00:23:15,920
♪ Throw a toy to
that bunch of brokers in town ♪

457
00:23:11,680 --> 00:23:12,480
I...

458
00:23:13,110 --> 00:23:15,000
will do it...

459
00:23:19,500 --> 00:23:22,100
♪ There's a strange, hazy feeling ♪

460
00:23:23,480 --> 00:23:25,060
♪ Waiting for me to make sense of it ♪

461
00:23:25,570 --> 00:23:27,850
♪ Worshippers hiding in the smoke,
just beyond reach ♪

462
00:23:30,130 --> 00:23:31,810
♪ They are all guests ♪

463
00:23:34,750 --> 00:23:36,400
♪ Be patient and wait ♪

464
00:23:41,830 --> 00:23:42,270
You...

465
00:23:43,070 --> 00:23:44,490
♪ Be patient and wait ♪

466
00:23:47,450 --> 00:23:49,100
♪ Be patient and wait ♪

467
00:23:53,200 --> 00:23:55,400
You really dealt with him with one hand.

468
00:24:13,750 --> 00:24:14,810
Comrade Fang Yong,

469
00:24:14,850 --> 00:24:16,050
there are some things

470
00:24:16,160 --> 00:24:17,100
we have to ask.

471
00:24:17,440 --> 00:24:19,250
Please come with us.

472
00:24:24,590 --> 00:24:25,170
Okay.

473
00:24:30,200 --> 00:24:30,810
How is it?

474
00:24:34,270 --> 00:24:35,210
Tell me.

475
00:24:38,310 --> 00:24:39,820
Good news and bad news—

476
00:24:40,240 --> 00:24:41,900
what do you want to hear first?

477
00:24:46,270 --> 00:24:47,800
The phone has been cracked.

478
00:24:48,510 --> 00:24:49,070
In one of

479
00:24:49,070 --> 00:24:50,530
Lang Bowen's past phones,

480
00:24:50,720 --> 00:24:52,160
there is a video Lang Bowen filmed

481
00:24:52,160 --> 00:24:53,760
during Chief Lu's accident.

482
00:24:54,720 --> 00:24:56,030
That video proved that

483
00:24:56,350 --> 00:24:57,950
Lang Bowen is just a witness.

484
00:24:57,960 --> 00:25:00,420
He can't be the murderer
who killed Chief Lu.

485
00:25:03,200 --> 00:25:04,920
Is this the good news or bad news?

486
00:25:04,920 --> 00:25:05,830
The bad news.

487
00:25:06,590 --> 00:25:07,990
What about the good news?

488
00:25:08,160 --> 00:25:09,690
The bad news is not over yet.

489
00:25:10,350 --> 00:25:10,960
Tell me.

490
00:25:11,720 --> 00:25:13,270
What were you going to do today?

491
00:25:13,270 --> 00:25:15,260
Rong said he couldn't leave today.

492
00:25:15,510 --> 00:25:17,310
He asked me to make a deal for him.

493
00:25:17,590 --> 00:25:19,450
It was all arranged by Hu Jianren.

494
00:25:19,830 --> 00:25:21,240
I don't know anything else.

495
00:25:21,240 --> 00:25:21,840
What deal?

496
00:25:22,480 --> 00:25:23,210
I don't know.

497
00:25:24,030 --> 00:25:25,430
I'm Mr. Zhou's employee.

498
00:25:25,920 --> 00:25:27,520
I went because he asked me to.

499
00:25:28,680 --> 00:25:30,270
You didn't ask what for?

500
00:25:30,350 --> 00:25:31,350
I ask Zhou Rong?

501
00:25:32,790 --> 00:25:33,550
He wouldn't

502
00:25:33,550 --> 00:25:35,210
have me do something illegal.

503
00:25:35,400 --> 00:25:37,350
I didn't do something illegal either.

504
00:25:37,350 --> 00:25:38,070
I don't know

505
00:25:38,070 --> 00:25:39,280
why I was arrested.

506
00:25:39,510 --> 00:25:40,640
You really don't know?

507
00:25:40,640 --> 00:25:41,160
I don't.

508
00:25:41,640 --> 00:25:42,350
I've always been

509
00:25:42,350 --> 00:25:43,510
an upright person.

510
00:25:43,640 --> 00:25:45,440
I will never accept your insult.

511
00:25:45,440 --> 00:25:46,640
Watch your attitude.

512
00:25:46,720 --> 00:25:48,010
Kill me!

513
00:25:48,510 --> 00:25:49,910
Still refusing to speak?

514
00:25:51,750 --> 00:25:52,680
I'm itchy.

515
00:25:52,830 --> 00:25:53,880
I'm itching.

516
00:25:54,480 --> 00:25:55,400
Just kill me—

517
00:25:55,750 --> 00:25:57,000
I will feel better!

518
00:25:58,110 --> 00:25:59,280
Did you give him allergy injection?

519
00:25:59,280 --> 00:25:59,990
Yes.

520
00:26:00,350 --> 00:26:00,960
But the doctor said

521
00:26:00,960 --> 00:26:02,110
it would take at least half an hour.

522
00:26:02,110 --> 00:26:03,310
Let me scratch!

523
00:26:03,310 --> 00:26:05,370
Stop flailing around. You won't die.

524
00:26:05,440 --> 00:26:06,240
Let me ask you.

525
00:26:06,880 --> 00:26:08,150
What's going on

526
00:26:08,310 --> 00:26:10,440
between Zhu Yifei, Zhou Rong, and you?

527
00:26:10,960 --> 00:26:13,440
I want to see Zhang Yi'ang.

528
00:26:13,880 --> 00:26:15,140
I'll only speak to him.

529
00:26:15,880 --> 00:26:17,240
Answer whatever's asked!

530
00:26:17,240 --> 00:26:18,920
This is not the place for you
to raise requests!

531
00:26:18,920 --> 00:26:20,310
Tell me about the night

532
00:26:20,310 --> 00:26:21,600
Ye Jian was killed.

533
00:26:22,200 --> 00:26:23,760
I've told you everything.

534
00:26:24,160 --> 00:26:25,480
I really don't know.

535
00:26:25,640 --> 00:26:26,370
Lu Yibo.

536
00:26:26,880 --> 00:26:28,000
Look at the situation you're in.

537
00:26:28,000 --> 00:26:28,590
Still not talking?

538
00:26:28,590 --> 00:26:29,590
If you don't believe me,

539
00:26:29,590 --> 00:26:31,390
there's nothing I can do either.

540
00:26:31,750 --> 00:26:32,700
What Xiaofei?

541
00:26:32,790 --> 00:26:33,550
I don't know him.

542
00:26:33,550 --> 00:26:35,160
Someone saw you together.

543
00:26:36,590 --> 00:26:37,790
Do you have evidence?

544
00:26:37,880 --> 00:26:38,940
You want evidence?

545
00:26:42,750 --> 00:26:43,610
Half a year ago,

546
00:26:43,790 --> 00:26:45,330
a car accident

547
00:26:45,400 --> 00:26:47,200
at a Sanjiangkou intersection.

548
00:26:47,200 --> 00:26:47,790
The victim is

549
00:26:47,790 --> 00:26:49,440
Deputy Chief of
the Sanjiangkou Public Security Bureau,

550
00:26:49,440 --> 00:26:50,080
Lu Zheng.

551
00:26:50,480 --> 00:26:51,480
Your phone

552
00:26:51,510 --> 00:26:52,640
filmed

553
00:26:52,640 --> 00:26:53,840
the whole accident.

554
00:26:54,550 --> 00:26:55,480
You don't remember?

555
00:26:55,480 --> 00:26:57,550
Three days after Chief Lu's accident,

556
00:26:57,550 --> 00:26:59,640
Rong Cheng transferred 30 million yuan

557
00:26:59,640 --> 00:27:01,340
project fee to Otto.

558
00:27:01,590 --> 00:27:02,160
Slander.

559
00:27:03,200 --> 00:27:04,730
This is a complete slander.

560
00:27:05,790 --> 00:27:07,440
You can check my bank.

561
00:27:08,030 --> 00:27:08,920
See how much money

562
00:27:08,920 --> 00:27:10,050
I have on my account.

563
00:27:10,200 --> 00:27:12,000
It's meaningless to waste time.

564
00:27:12,000 --> 00:27:13,260
Answer the questions.

565
00:27:13,640 --> 00:27:15,100
I want to see...
[Yi'ang.]

566
00:27:21,880 --> 00:27:23,350
That's a long bad news.

567
00:27:24,480 --> 00:27:25,790
What about the good news?

568
00:27:25,790 --> 00:27:27,920
Luckily there's Fang Chao and Liu Zhi.

569
00:27:28,030 --> 00:27:30,960
We were the perpetrators
of the provincial capital explosion case.

570
00:27:30,960 --> 00:27:31,690
It wasn't us.

571
00:27:31,880 --> 00:27:33,650
We also robbed the Land Rover.

572
00:27:33,720 --> 00:27:34,680
We both don't know how to drive.

573
00:27:34,680 --> 00:27:35,680
Why should we steal his car?

574
00:27:35,680 --> 00:27:36,720
I subdued that dude

575
00:27:36,720 --> 00:27:37,400
immediately.

576
00:27:37,400 --> 00:27:38,550
Don't believe that bastard.

577
00:27:38,550 --> 00:27:39,590
Nothing he says is true.

578
00:27:39,590 --> 00:27:40,890
But, just one thing—

579
00:27:41,110 --> 00:27:42,480
we didn't kill that dude

580
00:27:42,480 --> 00:27:43,880
who drove the Land Rover.

581
00:27:44,200 --> 00:27:45,440
My bro

582
00:27:46,200 --> 00:27:47,660
has never lied in his life.

583
00:27:49,590 --> 00:27:50,550
He did

584
00:27:50,550 --> 00:27:51,880
choked to his own death.

585
00:27:52,640 --> 00:27:54,850
The phone deal with Zhou Rong this time—

586
00:27:54,960 --> 00:27:57,330
my brother lured him away

587
00:27:57,510 --> 00:27:59,120
to have him get 20 million.

588
00:27:59,310 --> 00:28:01,210
Then he changed it to 5 million.

589
00:28:01,310 --> 00:28:03,270
At the end he charged
straight to his house

590
00:28:03,270 --> 00:28:05,250
to get 15 million.

591
00:28:06,030 --> 00:28:06,690
What a pity.

592
00:28:07,400 --> 00:28:08,730
With your bro's IQ,

593
00:28:08,790 --> 00:28:10,450
he can't make up such nosense.

594
00:28:10,720 --> 00:28:11,580
You were the one

595
00:28:11,750 --> 00:28:13,610
who came up with the ideas, right?

596
00:28:16,070 --> 00:28:16,640
Officer.

597
00:28:17,160 --> 00:28:17,880
Well...

598
00:28:19,830 --> 00:28:22,790
Can I get a reduced sentence
for reporting a corrupt official?

599
00:28:22,790 --> 00:28:24,310
That's Yu Yueran's calligraphy—

600
00:28:24,310 --> 00:28:25,570
how much's that worth?

601
00:28:26,030 --> 00:28:26,680
It's fake.

602
00:28:28,110 --> 00:28:29,470
Is this fake too?

603
00:28:36,110 --> 00:28:37,000
A Yuan Qinghua.

604
00:28:37,880 --> 00:28:39,880
Tripod cauldron with Chih-dragon handles.

605
00:28:39,880 --> 00:28:40,750
How much is it?

606
00:28:42,000 --> 00:28:43,060
This painting too.

607
00:28:43,310 --> 00:28:45,240
It's from when Qi Baishi was young.

608
00:28:45,720 --> 00:28:46,980
How much would that be?

609
00:28:47,720 --> 00:28:49,680
And the bed next door—

610
00:28:50,640 --> 00:28:52,100
do you dare to sleep on it?

611
00:28:57,000 --> 00:28:58,200
Fang Yong told Zhou Rong

612
00:28:58,200 --> 00:28:58,920
to trade for the East New Town project

613
00:28:58,920 --> 00:29:00,360
with bianzhong.

614
00:29:05,510 --> 00:29:06,380
Good.

615
00:29:06,830 --> 00:29:07,430
Very good.

616
00:29:07,680 --> 00:29:09,740
It'll be easier with this statement.

617
00:29:10,070 --> 00:29:10,600
Zhang,

618
00:29:10,720 --> 00:29:11,550
why did get down...

619
00:29:11,550 --> 00:29:12,420
I-I'm fine.

620
00:29:13,010 --> 00:29:13,880
Hearing good news,

621
00:29:13,880 --> 00:29:16,210
the wound doesn't hurt that much anymore.

622
00:29:23,680 --> 00:29:25,210
Don't be too old fashioned.

623
00:29:27,570 --> 00:29:28,630
Moving around more

624
00:29:29,030 --> 00:29:31,050
is the best way to recover.

625
00:29:31,720 --> 00:29:32,510
Look.

626
00:29:32,960 --> 00:29:34,560
I'm walking.

627
00:29:34,590 --> 00:29:36,160
Look at me.

628
00:29:36,680 --> 00:29:37,140
Look...

629
00:29:38,160 --> 00:29:38,890
Chief Zhang.

630
00:29:39,310 --> 00:29:40,610
It's nothing.

631
00:29:40,720 --> 00:29:41,950
It's okay.

632
00:29:42,030 --> 00:29:42,850
Turn around.

633
00:29:43,070 --> 00:29:44,000
Let's go another round.

634
00:29:44,000 --> 00:29:44,590
That's enough.

635
00:29:44,590 --> 00:29:45,200
I can do it!

636
00:29:45,270 --> 00:29:45,720
Come.

637
00:29:46,440 --> 00:29:47,170
Turn around.

638
00:29:53,480 --> 00:29:54,650
Slowly.

639
00:29:56,750 --> 00:29:57,490
Yi'ang.

640
00:29:58,310 --> 00:29:59,170
-Who—
-Yi'ang!

641
00:29:59,440 --> 00:30:00,060
Chief Qi.

642
00:30:00,110 --> 00:30:00,690
Wh-Why

643
00:30:00,720 --> 00:30:02,070
are you already walking?

644
00:30:02,070 --> 00:30:02,640
Here, here.

645
00:30:02,640 --> 00:30:03,900
I need to get used to it.

646
00:30:04,000 --> 00:30:05,080
You're being ridiculous.

647
00:30:05,080 --> 00:30:05,990
Seriously.

648
00:30:06,200 --> 00:30:07,510
Lie down.

649
00:30:07,510 --> 00:30:08,240
I'm fine. Seriously.

650
00:30:08,240 --> 00:30:08,680
Move.

651
00:30:08,880 --> 00:30:09,550
Lie down.

652
00:30:09,640 --> 00:30:10,160
Here.

653
00:30:10,400 --> 00:30:10,960
Be careful.

654
00:30:10,960 --> 00:30:11,830
-I'm fine.
-Slowly.

655
00:30:11,830 --> 00:30:12,350
Slowly.

656
00:30:12,480 --> 00:30:13,140
Be careful.

657
00:30:13,400 --> 00:30:14,000
Slowly.

658
00:30:14,070 --> 00:30:15,240
Slowly.

659
00:30:17,880 --> 00:30:18,440
See.

660
00:30:18,790 --> 00:30:20,320
-It's okay. Come on.
-Here.

661
00:30:20,640 --> 00:30:21,170
Okay.

662
00:30:22,920 --> 00:30:24,320
He wouldn't listen to me.

663
00:30:24,960 --> 00:30:25,640
See?

664
00:30:27,350 --> 00:30:28,440
Sit, Chief Qi. Sit.

665
00:30:28,590 --> 00:30:29,920
Sit, Captain Wang. Sit.

666
00:30:30,400 --> 00:30:31,950
Take it easy.

667
00:30:35,270 --> 00:30:36,800
How was the interrogation?

668
00:30:39,750 --> 00:30:40,820
How did it go?

669
00:30:42,550 --> 00:30:43,190
Not good.

670
00:30:43,790 --> 00:30:44,390
Not good.?

671
00:30:44,400 --> 00:30:45,600
The others went fine,

672
00:30:45,680 --> 00:30:46,480
but Zhou Rong—

673
00:30:46,790 --> 00:30:48,110
every time we asked him something,

674
00:30:48,110 --> 00:30:49,170
he asked to see you.

675
00:30:49,270 --> 00:30:50,690
Zhou Rong still thinks

676
00:30:51,480 --> 00:30:53,170
you were trying try harm him.

677
00:30:53,640 --> 00:30:54,350
This should be

678
00:30:54,350 --> 00:30:55,610
why he wants to see you.

679
00:30:59,270 --> 00:31:00,330
I do want to see him.

680
00:31:02,640 --> 00:31:03,170
Let's go!

681
00:31:03,770 --> 00:31:04,440
Where are you going?

682
00:31:04,440 --> 00:31:05,110
I'm fine!

683
00:31:05,640 --> 00:31:06,480
Chief Qi said

684
00:31:06,480 --> 00:31:07,400
I can be discharged.

685
00:31:07,400 --> 00:31:08,330
Right, Chief Qi?

686
00:31:08,550 --> 00:31:10,210
Take me to the 4th floor first.

687
00:31:11,070 --> 00:31:16,220
♪ Doubt ♪

688
00:31:15,920 --> 00:31:16,480
Hu Jianren

689
00:31:16,480 --> 00:31:17,870
was sentenced to a year

690
00:31:17,920 --> 00:31:18,920
for assault.

691
00:31:19,070 --> 00:31:20,030
Zhou Rong went to Chief Lu

692
00:31:19,520 --> 00:31:24,940
♪ Doubt ♪

693
00:31:20,070 --> 00:31:21,440
to help ease this situation.

694
00:31:21,440 --> 00:31:23,480
But Chief Lu insists on his principles.

695
00:31:23,480 --> 00:31:24,340
We suspect that

696
00:31:24,440 --> 00:31:26,270
he held a grudge against Chief Lu,

697
00:31:26,270 --> 00:31:28,130
so he hired Lang Bowen to kill him.

698
00:31:29,110 --> 00:31:43,450
♪ Doubt, doubt the doubt ♪

699
00:31:29,880 --> 00:31:30,670
Also,

700
00:31:31,000 --> 00:31:32,440
why were two deals

701
00:31:32,550 --> 00:31:34,550
going on at the same time yesterday?

702
00:31:34,750 --> 00:31:36,350
Why didn't Zhou Rong show up?

703
00:31:37,460 --> 00:31:39,030
This is a mess.

704
00:31:40,270 --> 00:31:40,790
Yi'ang,

705
00:31:41,480 --> 00:31:43,280
do you think you can do anything?

706
00:31:44,070 --> 00:31:45,310
No matter how cunning a hunter is,

707
00:31:45,310 --> 00:31:46,770
they're no match for a fox.

708
00:31:52,780 --> 00:31:54,580
I think he got that saying wrong.

709
00:31:55,110 --> 00:31:56,190
Focus on the road.

710
00:32:10,440 --> 00:32:11,640
I'll leave the rest

711
00:32:11,960 --> 00:32:12,880
to you.

712
00:32:13,510 --> 00:32:14,750
Chief Qi, don't worry.

713
00:32:14,750 --> 00:32:15,550
Please go ahead.

714
00:32:15,550 --> 00:32:15,960
Okay.

715
00:32:16,070 --> 00:32:16,830
I'm heading back to my office first.

716
00:32:16,830 --> 00:32:17,200
Okay.

717
00:32:21,680 --> 00:32:22,410
Chief Zhang,

718
00:32:22,830 --> 00:32:24,890
you have a way to make Zhou Rong speak?

719
00:32:25,270 --> 00:32:26,860
I don't for now.

720
00:32:27,440 --> 00:32:28,350
But you just said—

721
00:32:28,350 --> 00:32:30,750
I can't say I have nothing for now
to my boss.

722
00:32:31,240 --> 00:32:31,900
Be careful.

723
00:32:33,640 --> 00:32:34,440
Captain Wang!

724
00:32:36,310 --> 00:32:37,640
Captain Wang, it's me!

725
00:32:45,720 --> 00:32:47,180
Where do you think this is?

726
00:32:47,480 --> 00:32:48,410
A bar?

727
00:32:48,790 --> 00:32:49,610
Take it back.

728
00:32:49,790 --> 00:32:50,590
Brother Wang,

729
00:32:51,000 --> 00:32:51,750
please help.

730
00:32:52,480 --> 00:32:53,590
Yibo can't sleep at night

731
00:32:53,590 --> 00:32:54,550
if he doesn't drink a little.

732
00:32:54,550 --> 00:32:57,010
He can fall asleep when
he has a peace of mind.

733
00:32:57,070 --> 00:32:57,510
Also,

734
00:32:57,510 --> 00:32:58,640
you can call me by my name—

735
00:32:58,640 --> 00:32:59,550
Captain Wang's good too.

736
00:32:59,550 --> 00:33:00,510
Don't call me Brother Wang.

737
00:33:00,510 --> 00:33:02,310
Where did the brother come from?

738
00:33:02,790 --> 00:33:04,990
You are not allowed to give gifts, okay?

739
00:33:05,110 --> 00:33:05,680
Got it.

740
00:33:08,510 --> 00:33:09,660
How is Yibo now?

741
00:33:09,960 --> 00:33:11,230
I can't tell you.

742
00:33:12,440 --> 00:33:13,240
Captain Wang.

743
00:33:13,590 --> 00:33:14,350
I know Yibo

744
00:33:14,350 --> 00:33:16,080
wouldn't dare to say anything.

745
00:33:16,550 --> 00:33:17,950
This is really not on him.

746
00:33:18,160 --> 00:33:19,560
He's afraid of Zhou Rong.

747
00:33:19,680 --> 00:33:21,280
It's useless to tell me this.

748
00:33:22,310 --> 00:33:23,310
We follow the law.

749
00:33:28,530 --> 00:33:32,130
[Sanjiangkou Public Security Bureau]

750
00:33:41,750 --> 00:33:42,880
Zhou Rong, come out.

751
00:33:50,030 --> 00:33:50,880
Chief Zhang

752
00:33:51,160 --> 00:33:52,760
is finally showing his face?

753
00:33:53,350 --> 00:33:54,280
How did you know?

754
00:34:06,480 --> 00:34:06,920
Weird.

755
00:34:07,830 --> 00:34:09,550
No one told him.

756
00:34:09,840 --> 00:34:10,940
How did he know

757
00:34:11,150 --> 00:34:12,760
that it's Chief Zhang interrogating him?

758
00:34:12,760 --> 00:34:13,290
Officer.

759
00:34:15,590 --> 00:34:16,750
Excuse me.

760
00:34:17,230 --> 00:34:19,159
What's the weather like tomorrow?

761
00:34:21,800 --> 00:34:22,530
Will it rain?

762
00:34:23,110 --> 00:34:24,510
Will the winds be strong?

763
00:34:24,550 --> 00:34:26,219
I left my laundry outside.

764
00:34:27,150 --> 00:34:28,230
Help me check it up.

765
00:34:38,320 --> 00:34:38,960
Help me

766
00:34:39,710 --> 00:34:40,840
remove this needle.

767
00:34:41,280 --> 00:34:42,150
Don't you have to go back to the hospital

768
00:34:42,150 --> 00:34:43,750
to get your injection later?

769
00:34:43,840 --> 00:34:45,310
I'd look weak like this.

770
00:34:46,030 --> 00:34:46,690
Pull it out.

771
00:34:49,590 --> 00:34:50,070
Take it.

772
00:34:51,800 --> 00:34:52,800
Two, one. Go.

773
00:35:00,030 --> 00:35:01,490
You're here, Chief Zhang.

774
00:35:02,000 --> 00:35:03,000
How is your injury?

775
00:35:03,000 --> 00:35:03,530
I'm fine.

776
00:35:04,030 --> 00:35:05,360
I just lost my appendix.

777
00:35:05,400 --> 00:35:06,150
You know I'm injured,

778
00:35:06,150 --> 00:35:07,630
yet you insisted on seeing me.

779
00:35:07,630 --> 00:35:08,710
I'm injured too.

780
00:35:08,710 --> 00:35:10,310
I wasn't allowed to lie down.

781
00:35:10,840 --> 00:35:11,920
Then let's quickly

782
00:35:12,030 --> 00:35:13,400
clear things up.

783
00:35:13,840 --> 00:35:15,830
I'll try my best

784
00:35:15,960 --> 00:35:16,840
to get you

785
00:35:16,840 --> 00:35:18,180
the best results.

786
00:35:18,670 --> 00:35:19,670
If we wrap this up quickly,
you can go to bed

787
00:35:19,670 --> 00:35:20,400
early.

788
00:35:20,510 --> 00:35:21,610
Think I'm a kid?

789
00:35:22,110 --> 00:35:22,630
Best

790
00:35:22,630 --> 00:35:23,630
results?

791
00:35:24,110 --> 00:35:25,510
Make two death penalties

792
00:35:25,510 --> 00:35:26,520
into one?

793
00:35:28,000 --> 00:35:29,860
Why are you so eager to see me then?

794
00:35:32,320 --> 00:35:32,960
Be honest.

795
00:35:34,110 --> 00:35:35,570
You planted so many people

796
00:35:35,670 --> 00:35:36,880
around me—

797
00:35:37,840 --> 00:35:39,260
what's your purpose?

798
00:35:40,030 --> 00:35:41,440
To obey the law.

799
00:35:42,000 --> 00:35:42,730
Drop the act!

800
00:35:43,440 --> 00:35:44,150
Sanjiangkou

801
00:35:44,150 --> 00:35:45,360
is all yours now, right?

802
00:35:45,360 --> 00:35:46,240
Your purpose is to

803
00:35:46,240 --> 00:35:47,240
end me.

804
00:35:47,480 --> 00:35:48,080
Zhou Rong.

805
00:35:48,150 --> 00:35:48,880
The interrogation room is not

806
00:35:48,880 --> 00:35:51,010
is not a place for you to talk nonsense.

807
00:35:51,190 --> 00:35:51,840
I'm sorry.

808
00:35:53,070 --> 00:35:53,880
I forgot...

809
00:35:54,800 --> 00:35:56,000
I forgot this is
the public security bureau.

810
00:35:56,000 --> 00:35:57,480
I can't talk like that, right?

811
00:35:57,480 --> 00:35:58,480
Understandable.

812
00:35:58,920 --> 00:36:00,400
The characteristics of his illness

813
00:36:00,400 --> 00:36:01,250
is

814
00:36:01,670 --> 00:36:02,410
suspicion

815
00:36:02,590 --> 00:36:03,990
and he easily gets angry.

816
00:36:04,710 --> 00:36:05,320
We can

817
00:36:05,320 --> 00:36:06,270
have a

818
00:36:06,360 --> 00:36:07,440
peaceful discussion

819
00:36:07,440 --> 00:36:08,190
as patients.

820
00:36:09,190 --> 00:36:09,710
Yes.

821
00:36:10,110 --> 00:36:11,370
We're in the same boat.

822
00:36:11,400 --> 00:36:11,960
Otherwise, why would our first meeting

823
00:36:11,960 --> 00:36:13,020
be in the hospital?

824
00:36:14,000 --> 00:36:14,410
No.

825
00:36:14,440 --> 00:36:16,100
Our illnesses are different—

826
00:36:16,230 --> 00:36:17,230
mine's an external one,

827
00:36:17,230 --> 00:36:18,760
and your is an internal one.

828
00:36:22,250 --> 00:36:22,990
Look.

829
00:36:23,510 --> 00:36:24,340
I got

830
00:36:24,380 --> 00:36:25,950
[Seek the truth; act according to the law]

831
00:36:24,800 --> 00:36:25,840
the psychiatrist on the 4th floor

832
00:36:25,840 --> 00:36:27,110
to prescribe this for you.

833
00:36:25,970 --> 00:36:27,910
[Be fair and civilized in law enforcement]

834
00:36:27,670 --> 00:36:28,710
This is the medicine your normally take

835
00:36:28,710 --> 00:36:30,370
to calm yourself down, right?

836
00:36:33,800 --> 00:36:35,440
Have you taken your medication today?

837
00:36:35,440 --> 00:36:35,920
Yes.

838
00:36:37,230 --> 00:36:39,230
Okay, let me help unravel it for you.

839
00:36:40,710 --> 00:36:42,240
In May the year before last,

840
00:36:42,900 --> 00:36:44,030
there was a fight

841
00:36:44,030 --> 00:36:45,060
in Fenglinwan.

842
00:36:50,000 --> 00:36:52,030
Hu Jianren was sentenced
to a year in prison

843
00:36:52,030 --> 00:36:53,590
for assault.

844
00:36:54,440 --> 00:36:55,070
This case

845
00:36:55,070 --> 00:36:56,530
was concluded by Chief Lu.

846
00:36:57,670 --> 00:36:58,570
Half a year ago,

847
00:36:58,840 --> 00:36:59,840
Chief Lu retired.

848
00:37:07,800 --> 00:37:09,460
The story of your destruction

849
00:37:09,480 --> 00:37:10,840
has then begun.

850
00:37:12,190 --> 00:37:13,230
Chief Lu

851
00:37:13,230 --> 00:37:14,480
has mentioned how unethical enterprises

852
00:37:14,480 --> 00:37:16,540
conspire with law enforcement staff

853
00:37:16,550 --> 00:37:18,330
to get benefits

854
00:37:18,440 --> 00:37:20,170
at various press conferences.

855
00:37:20,230 --> 00:37:22,030
Those were all about you, right?

856
00:37:23,550 --> 00:37:24,750
Why are you smirking?

857
00:37:24,960 --> 00:37:25,440
You...

858
00:37:26,360 --> 00:37:27,230
I understand.

859
00:37:28,440 --> 00:37:30,000
You left a mark
in the public security records—

860
00:37:30,000 --> 00:37:31,590
you were worried
that it'd affect your business.

861
00:37:31,590 --> 00:37:33,190
You were also worried that
you would lose your status

862
00:37:33,190 --> 00:37:34,030
in Sanjiangkou

863
00:37:34,030 --> 00:37:35,030
and you got angry.

864
00:37:35,110 --> 00:37:36,400
Did you make those threats

865
00:37:36,400 --> 00:37:37,230
because of these?

866
00:37:37,230 --> 00:37:38,200
Offering 30 million

867
00:37:38,200 --> 00:37:39,230
for Lu Zheng's life.

868
00:37:39,230 --> 00:37:39,830
Am I right?

869
00:37:40,480 --> 00:37:41,110
I killed him

870
00:37:41,110 --> 00:37:42,550
to avenge my brother.

871
00:37:43,400 --> 00:37:45,130
He locked Hu up for a whole year.

872
00:37:45,190 --> 00:37:46,630
I went to beg him myself.

873
00:37:46,670 --> 00:37:48,670
He didn't give me any respect at all.

874
00:37:49,360 --> 00:37:50,240
Chief Lu!

875
00:37:50,670 --> 00:37:51,600
Chief Lu.

876
00:37:51,840 --> 00:37:52,400
That must've been tiring.

877
00:37:52,400 --> 00:37:53,230
You had to climb so many steps—

878
00:37:53,230 --> 00:37:55,290
why didn't they install an elevator?

879
00:37:55,440 --> 00:37:57,360
I'm Zhou Rong from Rongcheng Real Estate.

880
00:37:57,360 --> 00:37:58,510
I wanted to look for you at your office,

881
00:37:58,510 --> 00:37:59,030
but...

882
00:37:59,070 --> 00:38:00,590
I was afraid it would bring bad influence
to your reputation.

883
00:38:00,590 --> 00:38:01,110
Right?

884
00:38:01,470 --> 00:38:02,330
So...

885
00:38:02,630 --> 00:38:04,630
Why does he have to give you respect?

886
00:38:05,960 --> 00:38:06,960
Locking Hu Jianren up

887
00:38:06,960 --> 00:38:07,970
is by the law.

888
00:38:09,230 --> 00:38:10,410
No one

889
00:38:10,550 --> 00:38:11,650
can change it.

890
00:38:13,150 --> 00:38:14,680
There was something worse.

891
00:38:14,800 --> 00:38:15,520
Lu,

892
00:38:15,800 --> 00:38:16,800
after you retire,

893
00:38:16,920 --> 00:38:17,840
who do you think

894
00:38:17,880 --> 00:38:19,240
should take over you?

895
00:38:19,760 --> 00:38:20,540
How is Ye?

896
00:38:29,630 --> 00:38:30,430
Lu Zheng

897
00:38:30,760 --> 00:38:32,290
hindered Ye Jian's future.

898
00:38:33,800 --> 00:38:35,400
Ye Jian was a good cop, right?

899
00:38:36,070 --> 00:38:37,400
He never took a penny from me.

900
00:38:37,400 --> 00:38:39,040
He never did anything for me.

901
00:38:39,070 --> 00:38:41,070
He was held back because of Lu Zheng!

902
00:38:42,070 --> 00:38:44,070
Ye Jian was indeed a good policeman.

903
00:38:44,630 --> 00:38:45,740
We all know that.

904
00:38:46,030 --> 00:38:46,960
But I want to know

905
00:38:47,480 --> 00:38:48,890
who told you

906
00:38:49,280 --> 00:38:50,880
Lu Zheng was against Ye Jian?

907
00:38:52,190 --> 00:38:53,360
He never once did.

908
00:38:55,110 --> 00:38:56,740
Cheif Qi told me about this.

909
00:38:57,960 --> 00:38:59,260
He is a talent.

910
00:38:59,710 --> 00:39:01,510
We should send him out to learn.

911
00:39:02,000 --> 00:39:03,360
It's a pity for him

912
00:39:03,880 --> 00:39:05,210
to stay in Sanjiangkou.

913
00:39:10,000 --> 00:39:11,070
You mean I...

914
00:39:11,230 --> 00:39:12,360
By killing Lu Zheng,

915
00:39:12,670 --> 00:39:14,570
I held Ye Jian back too?

916
00:39:15,920 --> 00:39:17,250
I didn't mean that. I...

917
00:39:18,250 --> 00:39:18,800
Lu Zheng's death

918
00:39:18,800 --> 00:39:20,260
has nothing to do with you.

919
00:39:21,190 --> 00:39:23,050
Lu Zheng's death was an accident.

920
00:39:24,760 --> 00:39:25,480
We didn't have any evidence

921
00:39:25,480 --> 00:39:26,710
at first.

922
00:39:27,000 --> 00:39:27,880
But this is interesting.

923
00:39:27,880 --> 00:39:29,280
We haven't done anything

924
00:39:29,400 --> 00:39:30,230
coming to Sanjiangkou—

925
00:39:30,230 --> 00:39:30,880
all we saw were you lot

926
00:39:30,880 --> 00:39:32,000
running up and down

927
00:39:32,000 --> 00:39:33,330
trying to cover the murder evidence.

928
00:39:33,330 --> 00:39:35,000
I-It was quite ridiculous.

929
00:39:36,590 --> 00:39:37,050
Well...

930
00:39:38,150 --> 00:39:38,440
Wait.

931
00:39:38,440 --> 00:39:39,630
Th-The evidence in the phone

932
00:39:39,630 --> 00:39:40,670
i-is fake?

933
00:39:44,480 --> 00:39:46,340
Lang Bowen w-was messing with me?

934
00:39:47,400 --> 00:39:48,550
Lang Bowen filmed the crime scene

935
00:39:48,550 --> 00:39:49,960
with his phone.

936
00:39:50,030 --> 00:39:51,070
But it was also a coincidence

937
00:39:51,070 --> 00:39:52,070
that he filmed it.

938
00:39:52,840 --> 00:39:54,590
All he did was bring this phone to you

939
00:39:54,590 --> 00:39:55,440
to cheat a huge sum of money

940
00:39:55,440 --> 00:39:55,970
from you.

941
00:40:05,760 --> 00:40:06,290
Then I...

942
00:40:06,960 --> 00:40:09,990
I wasted my time with those two idiots.

943
00:40:11,150 --> 00:40:12,360
I can also tell you

944
00:40:12,800 --> 00:40:14,400
Du Cong is not someone I planted.

945
00:40:14,400 --> 00:40:15,590
Neither is Fang Chao and Liu Zhi.

946
00:40:15,590 --> 00:40:16,550
I didn't arrange for Officer Li

947
00:40:16,550 --> 00:40:18,010
to go to your house either.

948
00:40:18,670 --> 00:40:19,150
W-Wait.

949
00:40:19,150 --> 00:40:20,920
That's not what you said yesterday.

950
00:40:20,920 --> 00:40:21,920
What should I believe,

951
00:40:21,920 --> 00:40:22,400
Zhang Yi'ang?

952
00:40:22,400 --> 00:40:23,000
I didn't do

953
00:40:23,000 --> 00:40:23,960
these things, then.

954
00:40:23,960 --> 00:40:25,090
I won't admit it now.

955
00:40:25,550 --> 00:40:27,480
You can believe whatever you want.

956
00:40:29,070 --> 00:40:30,320
If you didn't do these,

957
00:40:30,320 --> 00:40:31,230
then let's talk about

958
00:40:31,230 --> 00:40:32,630
what you've done before.

959
00:40:33,280 --> 00:40:34,940
Speculating cultural relics

960
00:40:35,150 --> 00:40:36,440
and illegal arms possession.

961
00:40:36,440 --> 00:40:38,000
In order to get the East New Town project,

962
00:40:38,000 --> 00:40:38,960
you bribed officials

963
00:40:38,960 --> 00:40:39,670
and assaulted the police.

964
00:40:39,670 --> 00:40:40,870
You did these, right?

965
00:40:41,510 --> 00:40:43,360
There's also Hu Jianren
trying to get kickbacks,

966
00:40:43,360 --> 00:40:45,150
Du Cong using the company car
for his own use,

967
00:40:45,150 --> 00:40:46,550
Lu Yibo reporting his private life
being a mess...

968
00:40:46,550 --> 00:40:48,150
All right, stop right there.

969
00:40:48,550 --> 00:40:49,230
They are ungrateful!

970
00:40:49,230 --> 00:40:51,230
Trying to get me from behind my back.

971
00:40:51,230 --> 00:40:52,690
No one is trying to get you.

972
00:40:54,320 --> 00:40:55,030
But you were

973
00:40:55,030 --> 00:40:56,830
indeed dragged down by someone.

974
00:40:57,960 --> 00:40:58,820
You, yourself.

975
00:41:06,510 --> 00:41:07,030
Chief.

976
00:41:07,960 --> 00:41:09,160
The rest will be easy.

977
00:41:09,510 --> 00:41:10,670
Interrogate them seperately.

978
00:41:10,670 --> 00:41:11,110
Okay.

979
00:41:11,660 --> 00:41:16,390
[Interrogation Rooms]

980
00:41:17,360 --> 00:41:17,920
Chief.

981
00:41:19,550 --> 00:41:20,120
I'm fine.

982
00:41:21,030 --> 00:41:21,560
I'm fine.

983
00:41:23,400 --> 00:41:24,200
Captain Wang!

984
00:41:24,480 --> 00:41:25,810
Zhou Qi wants to see you.

985
00:41:25,840 --> 00:41:27,040
Why is she still here?

986
00:41:27,840 --> 00:41:28,320
I'll go take a look.

987
00:41:28,320 --> 00:41:28,710
Okay.

988
00:41:35,810 --> 00:41:36,540
Chief Zhang,

989
00:41:36,960 --> 00:41:38,550
don't make it difficult for me.

990
00:41:38,550 --> 00:41:40,210
I really don't know anything.

991
00:41:42,590 --> 00:41:44,390
Because you reported Zhou Rong,

992
00:41:45,000 --> 00:41:46,930
yet Zhou Rong chose to forgive you,

993
00:41:47,840 --> 00:41:49,160
you decided to do the trade for him

994
00:41:49,160 --> 00:41:50,690
to make up for your mistake?

995
00:41:52,320 --> 00:41:53,030
Am I right?

996
00:41:55,630 --> 00:41:57,360
Let me tell you the latest news:

997
00:41:58,760 --> 00:42:00,760
Zhou Rong confessed to everything.

998
00:42:13,440 --> 00:42:13,880
Chief.

999
00:42:13,920 --> 00:42:14,230
Chief.

1000
00:42:14,230 --> 00:42:14,630
You...

1001
00:42:14,960 --> 00:42:16,020
Excuse me. Wait up.

1002
00:42:16,070 --> 00:42:16,930
What happened?

1003
00:42:17,000 --> 00:42:17,550
Zhou Qi is here.

1004
00:42:17,550 --> 00:42:18,920
She provided an important clue.

1005
00:42:18,920 --> 00:42:20,320
Before Lu Yibo went for the deal,

1006
00:42:20,320 --> 00:42:20,880
he asked her...

1007
00:42:20,880 --> 00:42:22,810
To go look for Lang Bowen directly.

1008
00:42:24,110 --> 00:42:25,630
Lu Yibo confessed everything.

1009
00:42:25,630 --> 00:42:26,560
What did you say?

1010
00:42:26,880 --> 00:42:27,500
Chief.

1011
00:42:27,590 --> 00:42:28,520
-Chief.
-You...

1012
00:42:28,590 --> 00:42:29,650
Excuse me. Wait up.

1013
00:42:30,230 --> 00:42:31,490
Hu Jianren confessed.

1014
00:42:31,550 --> 00:42:32,410
What did he say?

1015
00:42:32,430 --> 00:42:34,190
He basically evidenced
what Zhou Rong said.

1016
00:42:34,190 --> 00:42:34,960
He said Captain Ye's death

1017
00:42:34,960 --> 00:42:36,110
has nothing to do with them.

1018
00:42:36,110 --> 00:42:36,760
They also told us

1019
00:42:36,760 --> 00:42:38,160
how they killed Xiaofei.

1020
00:42:41,030 --> 00:42:41,630
Help me up.

1021
00:42:42,820 --> 00:42:44,670
We'll go interrogate Lang Bowen right now.

1022
00:42:44,670 --> 00:42:45,110
Sorry.

1023
00:42:45,150 --> 00:42:46,150
What did you say just now?

1024
00:42:46,150 --> 00:42:47,740
You need to stay in bed.

1025
00:42:48,190 --> 00:42:49,150
I'll go interrogate them first.
